Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安\N（2019年  初春都内某摄影棚）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.37,0:00:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到内裤里  太短了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么   简单的跟大家打个招呼  可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的我是s1专属女优  桥本有菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要拍摄什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天啊，听说是口交\N（口交）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  大概是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该是擅长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.21,0:00:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么对于女性来说，你对口交的觉醒是什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.81,0:00:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢，这个，我的话，中学的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.42,0:01:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候就第一次看了av
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.76,0:01:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候就很感兴趣，想要试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.49,0:01:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候就感兴趣想试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.16,0:01:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,属于研究型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的，这个，虽然不能这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.04,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是想研究一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有自信吗？有自信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.38,0:01:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天啊，我么拍摄有菜的口交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不发射，忍得住的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不发射，忍得住可以做爱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.53,0:01:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有拍摄过只是用嘴射出来吧   有的，有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，好难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.48,0:01:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的哦，好难，但是有时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.61,0:02:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一个人都没办法完成做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后怎么办？再来一次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是更好吗？真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做到色情的口交吧   色情的口交？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 试试可以吧  不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色情口交  是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，太快了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.12,0:02:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，大家都已经集中在那边等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个，我听到声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.40,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，稍等一下几分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.53,0:02:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四分钟啊，好的，大家都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是和我的   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给自己打打气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对寇家还是比较有自信的，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.69,0:03:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（口交女神桥本vs绝对想要做爱的17名素人）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.83,0:03:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在等有菜登场的各位）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.05,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，现在，我们开始拍摄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  请大家多多的关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道要做什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了做很色情的事情是吧  是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好色的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，白色那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布的后面写着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备，来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.62,0:04:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（你能忍住桥本有菜的口交吗？）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，大家读一下这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦，预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.23,0:04:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能忍住，桥本有菜的口交吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.91,0:04:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样，可以忍住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.25,0:04:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，我没你已经写了一个问号了，能否忍住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AV哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的。做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家，想做爱得人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以忍住得人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能够忍住吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和有菜做爱吧    是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，我们叫她出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦，预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，有菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是   和大家打个招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，我是桥本有菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位，谢谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.09,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家想和我做爱吗？想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，在这之前，能够忍住口交吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.17,0:06:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了，这个，糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.38,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，各位，很好忍住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，各位加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.72,0:07:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，那么，这个啊，有菜在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说明一下，一开始的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位，开始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，大家仔细听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.41,0:07:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先，忍住一分钟的人将通过预选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家到这里排队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.82,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（口交初次预选     一个分钟口交挑战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.43,0:07:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样，是不是很紧张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了，这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有自信吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然有了   多少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少呢，这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，十个，十个左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不会有这么多吧       非常不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望大家加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.99,0:08:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，开始了哦 ，一个个来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，开始了哦，   好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，开始了，预备，开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了，忍住一分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了，好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了三十秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.92,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五四三一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的有点难啊   是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么继续吧   好的，下一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的   麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦，预备，开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.62,0:09:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下   不行，不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.37,0:10:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，不行啊    过了三十秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.40,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五四三二一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.07,0:10:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.14,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，下一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦，预备，开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.75,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有五秒   真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.23,0:12:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个可以吗？两个一起  虽然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，不利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个，过来吧   好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？   这个可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦    可以是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双手不行，不能打手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，预备，开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人在休息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了   真的不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.34,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，慢一点可以吧   慢一点就没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了  这样的话，没办法射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.76,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.83,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.37,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五四三二一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.58,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行 我说了不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.85,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不行吧   恭喜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.19,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，一个个来吧   一个个来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，下一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦   这次加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
