Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.57,0:41:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢啊，好的，无套，无套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.64,0:41:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.51,0:41:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:21.18,0:41:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多久没射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:23.85,0:41:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后摸乳头，差点忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.65,0:41:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.99,0:41:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.39,0:41:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，接下来就要做爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.46,0:41:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.86,0:41:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.73,0:41:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，接下来的话   接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.87,0:41:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.27,0:41:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，来吧，请     请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.27,0:41:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照   请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.41,0:41:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照   请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.08,0:41:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以问一下你叫什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.88,0:42:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么？  我叫川崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.28,0:42:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,川崎是吧   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:01.75,0:42:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照   请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.42,0:42:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.09,0:42:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里，可以做爱哦   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.49,0:42:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做爱  想做是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.29,0:42:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，要忍住啊   好的
