Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.63,0:42:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.50,0:42:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然做爱很好  但是，舒服是最重要的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.11,0:42:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的吧，这个的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.38,0:42:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱是不是
