Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.15,0:43:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男的很喜欢的 可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.82,0:43:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了   糟糕了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.02,0:43:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系的，只是这样而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.36,0:43:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦，那么，准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.56,0:43:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备，开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.25,0:43:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.07,0:44:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.55,0:44:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
